o 10 lat więzienia","Mogło dojść do zanieczyszczenia jednej z największych rzek w woj. łódzkim?","2026-03-06 14:39:47",{"comments":61},{"aid":1163,"attachments":1164,"category":1176,"category_id":83,"featured":61,"id":1177,"is_redirect":61,"lead":1178,"locked":61,"origin_domain":1179,"parent_domain":1179,"parent_id":1180,"premium":61,"priority":51,"published":51,"published_at":1181,"recommended":61,"redirect_url":1182,"short_title":1183,"slug":1184,"sponsored":33,"sub_title":1185,"title":1186,"uid":1177,"updated_at":1187,"stats":1188,"is_photostory":61,"is_advertisement":61,"is_pool":61,"show_quiz_cover":33,"view_type":848},12133,{"id":1165,"name":98,"url":1166,"thumbnail":98,"created_at":1167,"tags":98,"author":825,"type":826,"filename":1168,"description":1169,"750x750px":1170,"160x90px":1171,"365x225px":1172,"100x100px":1173,"760xautopx":1174,"1200x675px":1175},16501,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/5f466fc9-2d2f-417c-ace9-bce14a436489","2026-03-06 12:10:22","5f466fc9-2d2f-417c-ace9-bce14a436489","Rewolucja w egzaminach na prawo jazdy. Kandydaci trafią do symulatorów","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/409d2377-32eb-447c-a9c3-ddf410cae59a","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/38c532a3-ae22-423a-bb44-e5ff8964397d","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/817f052e-0951-4660-89d5-77d42f48f6e4","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/3dc3ea25-f723-470b-a627-fb9c50cb7ce0","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/3bb17990-7217-4154-a7fa-414ece2fa01a","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/trybunalski/articles/image/77c6a42f-387e-4612-9b30-06d581fd1060",[125,144],"JS1WGeiLjNMig5wF3cLY","Polski system egzaminowania kierowców czekają istotne zmiany. Ministerstwo Infrastruktury przygotowuje przepisy, które wprowadzą do egzaminu na prawo jazdy nowy element – test percepcji ryzyka. Rozwiązanie ma sprawdzać zdolność przyszłych kierowców do rozpoznawania niebezpiecznych sytuacji na drodze i szybkiego reagowania na zagrożenia. Wszystko wskazuje na to, że zadanie będzie wykonywane na symulatorze jazdy, a jego wprowadzenie wynika z nowych wymogów Unii Europejskiej, które wszystkie państwa członkowskie muszą wdrożyć do 2026 roku.","trybunalski.pl","9nNFyW1FgWXEcpDHaYSe","2026-03-06 13:31:27","https://trybunalski.pl/region/nowy-element-w-egzaminach-na-prawo-jazdy-bedzie-kolejny-test-to-wymog-unijny/9nNFyW1FgWXEcpDHaYSe","Nowy element w egzaminach na prawo jazdy.","nowy-element-w-egzaminach-na-prawo-jazdy-bedzie-kolejny-test-to-wymog-unijny","Będzie kolejny test - to wymóg unijny","Rewolucja w egzaminach na prawo jazdy. Będzie kolejny test - to wymóg unijny","2026-03-06 14:34:57",{"comments":61},{"id":74,"config":1190,"variant":1191,"column":1192},{"color":808,"background":809},[794],[1193],{"module":1194,"size":794},[],{"id":83,"config":1196,"variant":1197,"column":1198},{"background":809,"color":911},[794],[1199],{"size":794,"module":1200},[],{"id":189,"config":1202,"variant":1204,"column":1205},{"background":1203,"color":808},"#BEBEBE",[138,138,138],[1206,1208,1210],{"size":138,"module":1207},[],{"module":1209,"size":138},[],{"module":1211,"size":138},[],{"variant":1213,"column":1214,"config":1223,"id":157},[794],[1215],{"module":1216,"size":794},[1217,1219,1220],{"name":65,"config":1218,"type":69},{"slot_id":338,"slot_view":68},{"name":85,"type":86},{"name":805,"type":806,"config":1221},{"link":59,"title":1222},"REGION",{"background":911,"color":1203},{"id":1225,"variant":1226,"column":1227,"config":1298},9,[138,138,138],[1228,1238,1266],{"module":1229,"size":138},[1230],{"config":1231,"name":57,"type":63,"articles":1233},{"mobile":59,"mobile_full":59,"limit":51,"mobile_intern":59,"type":853,"query":1232,"skip":61,"category":1232},"category:array-contains:region",[1234],{"aid":1163,"attachments":123