13,"size":138},[1314],{"name":57,"config":1315,"type":63,"articles":1317},{"mobile":59,"mobile_full":59,"mobile_intern":59,"type":853,"query":1316,"limit":51,"skip":61,"category":1316},"category:array-contains:rozmaitosci",[1318],{"aid":1319,"attachments":1320,"category":1331,"category_id":157,"featured":61,"id":1332,"is_redirect":61,"lead":1333,"locked":61,"origin_domain":27,"parent_domain":59,"parent_id":59,"premium":61,"priority":51,"published":51,"published_at":1334,"recommended":61,"redirect_url":59,"short_title":1335,"slug":1336,"sponsored":33,"sub_title":59,"title":1335,"uid":1332,"updated_at":1334,"stats":1337,"is_photostory":61,"is_advertisement":61,"is_pool":61,"show_quiz_cover":33,"view_type":848},11980,{"id":1321,"name":98,"url":1322,"thumbnail":98,"created_at":1323,"tags":98,"author":98,"type":826,"filename":1324,"description":98,"750x750px":1325,"160x90px":1326,"365x225px":1327,"100x100px":1328,"760xautopx":1329,"1200x675px":1330},16342,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/d8307e89-7a65-4a75-a835-5ab895cf83c4","2026-02-19 11:43:23","d8307e89-7a65-4a75-a835-5ab895cf83c4","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/c56a0c33-3d92-42d5-a027-bd79d619b4e6","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/6211193a-021b-4e17-a5b5-3cd9206cb2e4","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/5f97102d-91a9-4570-9d75-ef7b33c833aa","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/b6a92948-4bf1-427f-979b-0542ec8f5e31","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/8d0f30b2-2af4-4288-b872-0d7424c9d282","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/ddzelow/articles/image/3c0706b3-46c4-490e-a093-d6f1985f65e7",[153],"NoMZ5LXNO4FBfH1RvEae","Każdy rodzic w gminie Zelów marzy o tym, by jego dziecko miało dobry start w dorosłe życie. Czasami jednak droga do sukcesu wymaga dodatkowego wsparcia, nowoczesnego sprzętu lub pomocy fachowca. Właśnie teraz otwiera się wyjątkowa szansa dla naszych szkół, fundacji i urzędów. Dzięki wsparciu z Unii Europejskiej możemy wspólnie stworzyć projekty, które realnie odmienią codzienność uczniów i dadzą im narzędzia do budowania lepszej przyszłości.","2026-02-19 11:45:49","Zelów stawia na młodych. Fundusze Europejskie pomogą młodzieży rozwinąć skrzydła","zelow-stawia-na-mlodych-fundusze-europejskie-pomoga-mlodziezy-rozwinac-skrzydla",{"comments":61},{"module":1339,"size":138},[1340],{"name":57,"config":1341,"type":63,"articles":1342},{"mobile":59,"mobile_full":59,"mobile_intern":59,"type":853,"query":1316,"limit":51,"skip":51,"category":1316},[1343],{"aid":1344,"attachments":1345,"category":1358,"category_id":157,"featured":61,"id":1359,"is_redirect":61,"lead":1360,"locked":61,"origin_domain":838,"parent_domain":838,"parent_id":1361,"premium":61,"priority":704,"published":51,"published_at":1362,"recommended":61,"redirect_url":1363,"short_title":1364,"slug":1365,"sponsored":33,"sub_title":1366,"title":1367,"uid":1359,"updated_at":1368,"stats":1369,"is_photostory":61,"is_advertisement":61,"is_pool":61,"show_quiz_cover":33,"view_type":848},11362,{"id":1346,"name":98,"url":1347,"thumbnail":98,"created_at":1348,"tags":98,"author":1349,"type":826,"filename":1350,"description":1351,"750x750px":1352,"160x90px":1353,"365x225px":1354,"100x100px":1355,"760xautopx":1356,"1200x675px":1357},15706,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/0166ca2f-34bd-4cda-8a5c-0da4929cdd3c","2025-12-02 12:37:36","Pixabay","0166ca2f-34bd-4cda-8a5c-0da4929cdd3c","Ukryte zamienniki w kawie. Wysokie ceny przyciągają nieuczciwych sprzedawców","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/038e644e-7043-46ca-8b15-c9f657dcdb3b","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/ffae99ce-5949-4ef2-8a73-618ef5958422","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/14943374-e7a3-41fa-861b-225e9e40b40b","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/33b89878-bc11-4fb5-aaac-2b12dbddd127","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/453216bb-473c-4d62-a949-f0ede3544624","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/320cf10f-a52a-4363-9c26-e54a69d10292",[153],"bNZbBY0ResHqtC0uGGaE","Zjawisko fałszowania kawy narasta w miarę, jak ceny surowca osiągają kolejne rekordy. Praktyki te dotyczą zarówno tanich produktów, jak i imitacji marek premium, w których różnica między oryginałem a podróbką może być trudna do uchwycenia nawet dla doświadczonych konsumentów.","ISGOG7GxyrzmzbEGU65j","2025-12-07 15:33:25","https://ddbelchatow.pl/rozmaitosci/czesto-pijesz-kawe-uwaga-nie-daj-sie-nabrac-skala-problemu-rosnie/ISGOG7GxyrzmzbEGU65j","Uwaga na \"kawowe przekręty\".","czesto-pijesz-kawe-uwaga-nie-daj-sie-nabrac-skala-problemu-rosnie","Nie daj się nabrać","Często pijesz kawę? Uwaga, nie daj się nabrać. Skala problemu rośnie","2025-12-10 12:10:10",{"comments":61},{"module":1371,"size":138},[1372],{"name":57,"config":1373,"type":63,"articles":1374},{"mobile":59,"mobile_full":59,"mobile_intern":59,"type":853,"query":1316,"limit":51,"skip":103,"category":1316},[1375],{"aid":1376,"attachments":1377,"category":1389,"category_id":157,"featured":61,"id":1390,"is_redirect":61,"lead":1391,"locked":61,"origin_domain":838,"parent_domain":838,"parent_id":1392,"premium":61,"priority":704,"published":51,"published_at":1393,"recommended":61,"redirect_url":1394,"short_title":1395,"slug":1396,"sponsored":33,"sub_title":1397,"title":1398,"uid":1390,"updated_at":1399,"stats":1400,"is_photostory":61,"is_advertisement":61,"is_pool":61,"show_quiz_cover":33,"view_type":848},11134,{"id":1378,"name":98,"url":1379,"thumbnail":98,"created_at":1380,"tags":98,"author":825,"type":826,"filename":1381,"description":1382,"750x750px":1383,"160x90px":1384,"365x225px":1385,"100x100px":1386,"760xautopx":1387,"1200x675px":1388},15481,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/3abd68be-5bc8-4467-a5ce-42a27766f225","2025-11-13 17:03:19","3abd68be-5bc8-4467-a5ce-42a27766f225","Ta petycja uderza w programy socjalne. Oto co się zmieni","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/011225f7-750f-4bd4-84d6-c01cd0519337","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/d7d403bd-e99b-4238-a94a-8b1109679bea","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/437120df-3ae1-4be5-b925-2b5c9a0242ce","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/e017cced-ce3e-4dc4-832f-2bbf8c248c2e","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/bb6d2092-bfa8-44a1-91ad-55b6657f4794","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/898b040a-8597-479b-951d-55881067fe27",[153],"yHZbl5LCFnSrgLUzIGzD","Dyskusja o kształcie polityki społecznej powraca z nową siłą po złożeniu w parlamencie petycji, która kwestionuje dotychczasowy model finansowania państwa oraz sposób dystrybucji świadczeń. Autor dokumentu przekonuje, że radykalne zmiany mogłyby uprościć system i poprawić sytuację finansową obywateli, a jednocześnie nie zachwiałyby budżetem.","wYZhsdPZK4N8Ej5Q2E5f","2025-11-14 08:16:34","https://ddbelchatow.pl/rozmaitosci/koniec-13-i-14-emerytury-w-sejmie-pojawila-sie-odwazna-petycja/wYZhsdPZK4N8Ej5Q2E5f","Reformy, które mogą postawić domowy budżet na głowie.","koniec-13-i-14-emerytury-w-sejmie-pojawila-sie-odwazna-petycja","Petycja już w parlamencie","Koniec 13 i 14 emerytury? Petycja już w parlamencie","2025-11-14 14:20:46",{"comments":61},[138,138,138],{"background":809,"color":808},{"id":794,"config":1404,"variant":1405,"column":1406},{"background":809,"color":808},[178,178,178,178],[1407,1411,1441,1471],{"size":178,"module":1408},[1409],{"name":65,"config":1410,"type":69},{"slot_id":353,"slot_view":68},{"size":178,"module":1412},[1413],{"name":57,"config":1414,"type":63,"articles":1415},{"mobile":59,"mobile_full":59,"mobile_intern":59,"type":853,"query":1316,"limit":51,"skip":178,"category":1316},[1416],{"aid":1417,"attachments":1418,"category":1430,"category_id":157,"featured":61,"id":1431,"is_redirect":61,"lead":1432,"locked":61,"origin_domain":838,"parent_domain":838,"parent_id":1433,"premium":61,"priority":704,"published":51,"published_at":1434,"recommended":61,"redirect_url":1435,"short_title":1436,"slug":1437,"sponsored":33,"sub_title":59,"title":1438,"uid":1431,"updated_at":1439,"stats":1440,"is_photostory":61,"is_advertisement":61,"is_pool":61,"show_quiz_cover":33,"view_type":848},11122,{"id":1419,"name":98,"url":1420,"thumbnail":98,"created_at":1421,"tags":98,"author":1349,"type":826,"filename":1422,"description":1423,"750x750px":1424,"160x90px":1425,"365x225px":1426,"100x100px":1427,"760xautopx":1428,"1200x675px":1429},15469,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/c9493d81-ee30-4571-a16c-8da34fcd79fc","2025-11-12 13:42:54","c9493d81-ee30-4571-a16c-8da34fcd79fc","Tylko 7 dni urlopu i aż 18 dni wolnego w grudniu!","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/d3337426-ec2b-42f3-a66f-0422fd09f9ce","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/cb06bc7f-07e9-4963-8eba-22e0c6f464ec","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/58486897-1c61-4751-95bd-d3737ff4767e","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/46a104a9-b18b-4e4b-a23b-4a0fe46c7eb4","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/7a498d86-b41f-496c-97ee-9e0369ffd080","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/b3214ef0-eef2-4824-b87b-74abda2c1fc9",[153],"UC9hWpnRSMsvqWFl6q1I","Koniec roku to idealny moment, by zaplanować dłuższy urlop i zyskać więcej wolnego przy minimalnym wykorzystaniu dni z puli urlopowej. Układ kalendarza pozwala sprytnie połączyć święta, weekendy i dni ustawowo wolne od pracy, tworząc okazję do wyjątkowo długiego odpoczynku. Ci, którzy zaplanują go z wyprzedzeniem, mogą cieszyć się nawet 18 dniami wolnego, wykorzystując zaledwie siedem dni urlopu.","yED9BnCDVml4EGFEWBPF","2025-11-13 12:05:16","https://ddbelchatow.pl/rozmaitosci/wystarczy-kilka-dni-urlopu-by-odpoczywac-niemal-trzy-tygodnie-tak-zaplanujesz-grudzien-i-styczen/yED9BnCDVml4EGFEWBPF","Jak zaplanować święta i Nowy Rok, by odpoczywać prawie trzy tygodnie?","wystarczy-kilka-dni-urlopu-by-odpoczywac-niemal-trzy-tygodnie-tak-zaplanujesz-grudzien-i-styczen","Wystarczy kilka dni urlopu, by odpoczywać niemal trzy tygodnie. Tak zaplanujesz grudzień i styczeń","2025-11-14 14:18:40",{"comments":61},{"size":178,"module":1442},[1443],{"name":57,"config":1444,"type":63,"articles":1445},{"mobile":59,"mobile_full":59,"mobile_intern":59,"type":853,"query":1316,"limit":51,"skip":138,"category":1316},[1446],{"aid":1447,"attachments":1448,"category":1460,"category_id":157,"featured":61,"id":1461,"is_redirect":61,"lead":1462,"locked":61,"origin_domain":838,"parent_domain":838,"parent_id":1463,"premium":61,"priority":704,"published":51,"published_at":1464,"recommended":61,"redirect_url":1465,"short_title":1466,"slug":1467,"sponsored":33,"sub_title":1468,"title":1469,"uid":1461,"updated_at":1439,"stats":1470,"is_photostory":61,"is_advertisement":61,"is_pool":61,"show_quiz_cover":33,"view_type":848},11074,{"id":1449,"name":98,"url":1450,"thumbnail":98,"created_at":1451,"tags":98,"author":1349,"type":826,"filename":1452,"description":1453,"750x750px":1454,"160x90px":1455,"365x225px":1456,"100x100px":1457,"760xautopx":1458,"1200x675px":1459},15424,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/belchatow/articles/image/82191f51-ff7d-4fbd-8252-e48dbd183d82","2025-11-04 18:34:51","82191f51-ff7d-4fbd-8252-e48dbd183d82","Nowe przepisy już od stycznia 2026. Kto zyska dodatkowy urlop i wyższą odpra